# Task Description

## Problem Statement
Create a program that implements a structure called ZNAK with the following fields:
- Name - surname and first name
- ZOD - zodiac sign
- DATE - birth date (array of three numbers: year, month, day)

The program should:
- Input data from the keyboard into an array MASS consisting of 10 elements of type ZNAK
- Records must be sorted by birth date
- Display information about people born under a zodiac sign entered from the keyboard
- If no such person exists, display a message

## Implementation Details
- The program is structured according to the KIS-2 model (Client-Interface-Server)
- All files are organized according to the required project structure
- The code follows the C language coding standards
- Build automation is implemented with a Makefile


